api_list.name: daynight
api_list.description: Allows you to send an images in base64 or url and obtain a normalized percentage between 0.0 and 1.0 if the image was taken during the day or at night
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://day-night.p.rapidapi.com/daynight"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "day-night.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
